text: Jerry Lane was a baseball player. Jerry Lane or Layne may also refer to: *Gerry Lane (World War Z) *Jerry Layne, baseball umpire *Jerry Layne (ventriloquist) *Jerry Max Lane, writer of Gone as a Girl Can Get *Jeremiah 'Jerry' Lane of music duo, High Flyers *Geraldine 'Jerry' Lane, character in You're Only Young Once *Jeremy Lane (writer), also known as Jerry Lane ==See also== *Jeremy Lane (disambiguation)
